/////////////////////////////////////////////////// Where NOT to Open New Stores ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////


Setting 
https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@turf/turf@6/turf.min.js
https://unpkg.com/papaparse@5.3.2/papaparse.min.js
